' Modelo final del Observatorio Económico y de Mercados de Bolivia
' Fuente: elaboración propia basada en SDMX 3.1, GSIM 2.0, UN-NQAF e INE Bolivia.
' Archivo autónomo: no requiere includes externos.

@startuml
title Estado — methodology_version
skinparam shadowing false
[*] --> DRAFT
DRAFT --> TECHNICAL_REVIEW : submit
TECHNICAL_REVIEW --> DRAFT : corrections
TECHNICAL_REVIEW --> METHODOLOGICAL_REVIEW : technicalApproval
METHODOLOGICAL_REVIEW --> DRAFT : corrections
METHODOLOGICAL_REVIEW --> APPROVED : approve
METHODOLOGICAL_REVIEW --> REJECTED : reject
APPROVED --> PUBLISHED : publish
PUBLISHED --> SUPERSEDED : newVersionPublished
PUBLISHED --> WITHDRAWN : exceptionalWithdrawal
REJECTED --> DRAFT : reopen
SUPERSEDED --> [*]
WITHDRAWN --> [*]
@enduml
